                                <h5 id="fairness"class="faq-question"> <span class="faq-q">Q:</span>
                                    How will the platform ensure fair and objective results?
                                </h5>
                                <h5 class="faq-answer">
                                    The inspiration for the voting method we have developed is drawn from the nonprofit organization, <a href="http://intelligencesquaredus.org/about">Intelligence Squared US</a>, which has been conducting high-quality in-person debates using this format for over ten years. <br> <br>
                                    Additionally, we will be closely monitoring the growth of the community during this early adopter period to ensure that there is no manipulation of the voting system.
                                </h5>
